  "introText": "在声音世界里，你发现了独立的声音碎片。但这座新发现的工坊里有一些奇怪的机器——一种叫'合成器'的设备。它有两个输入端口和一个输出端口。如果把两个声音节点连到合成器的输入端，会发生什么？试试看！",
  "introTextEn": "In the Sound World, you discovered individual sound fragments. But this newly discovered workshop has strange machines — a device called a 'blender' with two inputs and one output. What happens if you connect two sound nodes to it? Try it!",
  "victoryText": "合成器发出了一种新的声音——/ma/！两个独立的声音碎片被'焊接'在了一起，形成了一个新的声音单元。这意味着：声音不是孤立存在的，它们可以像积木一样组合！",
  "victoryTextEn": "The blender produced a new sound — /ma/! Two independent sound fragments were 'welded' together into a new unit. This means: sounds don't exist in isolation — they can be combined like building blocks!",
